                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18150215-132-off784 t18150215-132-cd785"></join>, two sheets, value 7 s. a pair of shoes, value 10 s. a waistcoat, value 18 d. a handkerchief, value 6 d. and a cap, value 3 d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18150215-132-victim1106" type="victimName">
